text: Hypnodontopsis is a genus of haplolepideous mosses (Dicranidae) in family Rhachitheciaceae. It contains the following species (but this list may be incomplete): * Hypnodontopsis apiculata, Z. Iwats. & Nog. Category:Dicranales Category:Moss genera Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
